title: Hurricane Erick: Category 3 storm nears Mexico; southern states on high alert

title: Middle East crisis: Putin proposes peace talks between Iran and Israel; Trump tells him to focus on Ukraine first
description: Amid escalating Middle East tensions, Vladimir Putin offered Russia's mediation between Iran and Israel, citing Moscow's unique ties.
